Rating: 4
I made recipe X 1.5 and it scaled nicely. Do NOT increase the saffron though as it would surely overwhelm. Used real Spanish rice and fry those almonds good and brown for optimal flavor in the oil and prolonged crispness in the rice. Pre-plumped the currants in sherry/water. Guests raved and I am eating the scant leftovers for lunch as I write

